videos.description: A'ja Wilson passes across the court to Lindsey Spann in the corner who knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Cross-court pass leads to South Carolina 3-pointer

videos.description: Chennedy Carter hits the 3-pointer from the wing in the closing seconds of the 1st half.
videos.headline: Texas A&M 3-pointer closes the gap before halftime

videos.description: Texas A&M uses quick ball movement and gets it to Chennedy Carter who makes another 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Aggies break the press with 3-pointer

videos.description: A'ja Wilson rejects the shot on one end of the court, leading to the Tyasha Harris layup on the other end.
videos.headline: South Carolina block sets up fast-break bucket

videos.description: A'ja Wilson drives to the basket and hits the jumper in the paint to seal South Carolina's 61-59 win over Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Wilson banks in shot in closing seconds for South Carolina
